Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer 2/62 Barretta Road, Ravenhall, for lease.

The property sits within the Orbis Business Park. The estate is strategically located at the intersection of Riding Boundary Road and Robinsons Road in Ravenhall, Melbourne's fastest growing industrial precinct, 20km* west of Melbourne's CBD.

The estate is located within 1km* of the Robinsons Road exit/entry ramps to the Deer Park Bypass and provides strong logistics links through to Melbourne's CBD and beyond.

The immediate surrounding area comprises a mix of commercial, industrial and residential uses along with a strong local workforce with supporting services.

Key Property Features:
+  Total building area: 417sqm*
+  Clear span warehouse
+  LED warehouse lighting
+  Amenities on both levels
+  Enclosed kitchenette on ground floor
+  Air-conditioning
+  Reception area with reception desk
+  Security camera and alarm system
+  Sealed concrete warehouse floor
+  Male & female amenities
+  5 car parks
+  Vendor terms - flexible financing available 

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 1/17 Westwood Drive, Ravenhall, for lease.

1/17 Westwood Drive, Ravenhall will benefit from continuous exposure to passing traffic from neighbouring residential and commercial precincts. 

Westwood Drive/Robinsons Road/Palmers Road is a vital transport route for all occupiers in the western suburbs.

The property is located minutes from Robinsons Road interchange offering direct access to the Western Freeway and Western Ring Road. To the north, Ballarat Road is less than 750m* away which provides access to to the bulky goods retail precinct.

Property highlights include:
+ High-clearance 7m* clear span warehouse
+ Concrete tilt panel construction
+ Motorised container height RSD
+ Individual parking, yard and gate
+ Office over two levels
+ Tiled reception area
+ Bathrooms and tea room/kitchenette
+ No owners corporation

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate
